  participant A as Alice
  participant B as Bob
  participant C as Charlie

  A->>B: one
  B-->>A: four
  autonumber off

  alt unnumbered block
    A->>C: unnumbered
    C-->>A: ok
  else still unnumbered
    B->>C: ping
    C-->>B: pong
  end

